  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示runWhileNotFindAStopPoint这个核心流程是怎么工作的。关键点是它用了内存中的UnitOfWork来累积状态变更，而不是每次都直接写数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "runWhileNotFindAStopPoint",
        "estado",
        "tarefas",
        "eventos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Core先执行同步任务，然后创建UnitOfWork实例。这个UoW是在内存里累积所有变更对吧？包括状态、任务和事件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "em memória",
        "estado",
        "tarefas",
        "eventos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，完全正确。同步块执行完之后，Core才会调用commit，把UnitOfWork交给ProcessExecutionRepository去处理持久化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "commit",
        "unitOfWork"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我这样安排：Core到Repository是同步调用commit，然后Repository开启MongoDB事务，里面分三步：更新ProcessInstance、处理ExecutableTasks的创建和删除、最后把关键事件写入event_outbox。这样准确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository",
        "MongoDB",
        "ProcessInstance",
        "ExecutableTasks",
        "event_outbox",
        "criticalEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "准确。不过要注意，ExecutableTasks的创建和删除是合并在一个步骤里的，用\"Cria/Apaga\"表达就行。还有，event_outbox只收criticalEvents，不是全部事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ExecutableTasks",
        "Cria/Apaga",
        "event_outbox",
        "criticalEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把事务流程画好了。现在有个问题：commit成功后，Core还要异步发布事件对吧？这里应该用EventPublisher？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "EventPublisher",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，但注意EventPublisher也是内存中的，而且Core调用的是publishEvents，传入的是unitOfWork.lightweightEvents()——这些是轻量级事件，和写入outbox的criticalEvents不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "em memória",
        "publishEvents",
        "unitOfWork.lightweightEvents()",
        "lightweightEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "懂了，lightweightEvents是立即返回的，不需要等待实际发布完成。那Publisher到Core的返回要标注\"Retorno Imediato\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Publisher",
        "Core",
        "Retorno Imediato"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。还有，我注意到你之前写的是\"Repository到Core返回Commit成功\"，这个应该是虚线箭头表示异步返回对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository",
        "Core",
        "Commit bem-sucedido"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊对，我修正一下。Repository到Core的返回应该用虚线，表示这是commit操作的异步响应。还有MongoDB的事务提交返回给Repository也是虚线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository",
        "Core",
        "MongoDB",
        "COMMIT TRANSAÇÃO"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加个小细节：在同步块结束的地方加个Note，标注\"Fim do bloco síncrono\"，这样读图的人能清楚知道哪里是边界。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
